{"tid":1137151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批麥當勞標誌像女性胸部 女向法院提告要求精神賠償","createTime":"2019-05-03T14:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T01:58:32.000Z","uid":225846,"like":42,"dislike":585,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"46b08901b8191df7726c503e19791427d71b41dc","tid":1137151,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.seehua.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/132123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.seehua.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F132123.jpg&h=d2231dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯女子認為麥當勞的標誌像女性乳房，於是向法院提告。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯《uralinform》報導，俄羅斯女子科羅溫科娃( Anastasia Korovenkova)認為，麥當勞惡意使用女性大乳房當商標，損害女性消費者的精神狀態。<br />\n<br />\n她認為並非所有俄羅斯人都有大乳房，因此乳房小的女性會認為自己不正常。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，如果科羅溫科娃成功的話，那她可以獲得1萬盧布(約641令吉)的精神賠償費。"},{"pid":"734696d668c790a4ec74b00ffb4a122d9dde1938","tid":1137151,"uid":43063,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df52c31a9b83330d9b00246ed8cd95d670aeb9f5","tid":1137151,"uid":35430,"like":270,"dislike":2,"score":268,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"咁W呢？"},{"pid":"a997ca1c8e466e20cf2270684ceebaae35165db8","tid":1137151,"uid":46587,"like":122,"dislike":3,"score":119,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報導指出，如果科羅溫科娃成功的話，那她可以獲得1萬盧布(約641令吉)的精神賠償費。</blockquote><br />\n一千港紙夠睇咩精神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09c370805aee56bdc718aea30f39c3e7b420417","tid":1137151,"uid":166792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df52c31a9b83330d9b00246ed8cd95d670aeb9f5","tid":1137151,"uid":35430,"like":270,"dislike":2,"score":268,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:10:23.000Z",